code: @Override protected ShrinkAction doParseInstance(XContentParser parser) throws IOException {     return ShrinkAction.parse(parser). }
static ShrinkAction randomInstance() {     return new ShrinkAction(randomIntBetween(1, 100)). }

public void testNonPositiveShardNumber() {     Exception e = expectThrows(Exception.class, () -> new ShrinkAction(randomIntBetween(-100, 0))).     assertThat(e.getMessage(), equalTo("[number_of_shards] must be greater than 0")). }
